# Multi Text

## Summary

- Players enter multiple text answers
- Each configured answer is shown as its own required text input during play
- Players can receive partial score when only some inputs match
- Case sensitivity can be set per answer slot
- Whitespace can optionally be ignored when checking submitted text

## Use case

- Ask for several names, terms, or facts that must each be entered separately
- Award partial credit when players know some, but not all, required text answers
